1a:["$","section","2026-04-29",{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-5 pb-2 border-b border-border","children":"2026-yil 29-aprel"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-3","children":[["$","article","0",{"className":"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-5","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-foreground leading-snug mb-1.5","children":"IJPH endi JShShSdan alohida hisoblanadi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":"Ish haqi kalkulyatori va ish beruvchi xarajatlari yangilandi. IJPH 0,1% — bu JShShS 12% ustiga alohida ushlanma, uning bir qismi emas. Ish haqidan jami 12,1% ushlanadi (IT Park uchun 7,6%). Ilgari formula qo'lga 0,1% ko'p natija berardi."}]]}],["$","article","1",{"className":"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-5","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-foreground leading-snug mb-1.5","children":"Transport solig'i — yosh koeffitsiyenti tuzatildi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":"Ilgari eski avtomobillar kamroq soliq to'lardi — bu noto'g'ri edi. Soliq kodeksining 446-moddasiga ko'ra koeffitsiyent OSHIRILADI: 0–3 yil 1,0×, 3–7 yil 1,2×, 7–10 yil 1,4×, 10 yildan eski 1,5×. 10 yillik avtoga soliq endi to'g'ri hisoblanadi."}]]}],["$","article","2",{"className":"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-5","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-foreground leading-snug mb-1.5","children":"Umumiy rejimdagi YaTT — ijtimoiy soliq sof daromaddan 12%"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":"YaTT kalkulyatori endi haqiqiy ijtimoiy soliq yukini hisobga oladi: max(12 BHK minimum, sof daromaddan 12%). Ilgari faqat 12 BHK hisoblanardi — bu yuqori daromadli YaTTlar uchun soliq summasini kamaytirardi."}]]}],["$","article","3",{"className":"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-5","children":[["$","h